{"tid":2408739,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"馬英九、趙少康：應考慮中國疫苗","createTime":"2021-02-15T08:25:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T08:32:54.000Z","uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"21675dc513a3401396e7007610a88e4ab491e5ce","tid":2408739,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:25:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-02-14/536621\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2021-02-14%2F536621&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eeExUl64GHAvDQsppiVFus8%3D&h=d004bf9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-02-14/536621</a><br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情仍嚴峻，各國爭相訂購疫苗，雖然台灣疫情穩定，但在取得疫苗部分卻遇上困難，政府多次更改可取得疫苗的時間點。對此，前總統馬英九今（14）天表示，政府應該思考是否採用「中國疫苗」，能夠多一個來源不要放棄，不要立刻就拒絕，對國民健康的保障就多一分力量。<br />\n<br />\n依照目前最新消息，防疫指揮官陳時中表示，疫苗已經購入，約在年中可以拿到。回鍋國民黨的知名媒體人趙少康、國民黨主席江啟臣及馬英九今天共同到三重先嗇宮參拜，馬英九受訪時提到，關於台灣取得疫苗的時程，依照政府的說法還需要數個月，但疫情變化快速，台灣若能接受中國疫苗，能夠多一個來源不要放棄，不要立刻就拒絕，對國民健康的保障就多一分力量。<br />\n<br />\n趙少康也表示，蔡英文在春節談話時提到「疫情過後兩岸要和解、對話」，台灣總要表現一點善意，馬英九提出接受中國疫苗一事，其意思是「不要斷然拒絕，也不是一定要用」，如果將來能拿到別的有效疫苗，當然很好，如果沒有的話，也不要排斥，要用開放的態度。"},{"pid":"92376621cdfb9ad07cc45683b24c83fdbcb5e7c5","tid":2408739,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:29:37.000Z","msg":"韓粉應該優先打中國疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75fc1f31a8625a4829b7bcbfa2af170324b9c039","tid":2408739,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92376621cdfb9ad07cc45683b24c83fdbcb5e7c5","tid":2408739,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:29:37.000Z","msg":"韓粉應該優先打中國疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:30:44.000Z","msg":"打完之後順便送埋返去中國"},{"pid":"a55cea319b958fdedbc147235b2da6ba7be39143","tid":2408739,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:31:03.000Z","msg":"要敵人俾物資你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a510dfd93335691d9bf75899df0e0fe1eefbbeac","tid":2408739,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a55cea319b958fdedbc147235b2da6ba7be39143","tid":2408739,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:31:03.000Z","msg":"要敵人俾物資你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:32:03.000Z","msg":"佢哋嘅敵人係市民呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de7e15430d5af00b2bed463ed847b24f9e37b70","tid":2408739,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a55cea319b958fdedbc147235b2da6ba7be39143","tid":2408739,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:31:03.000Z","msg":"要敵人俾物資你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:32:54.000Z","msg":"非畀哦，係買，億億聲咁擲落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}